<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Station8 — Line Engine</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design.css">
</head>
<body>
{{> _nav }}

<div class="swe-container" style="padding-top: var(--space-xxl); padding-bottom: var(--space-section);">

    <!-- Hero stripe -->
    <div class="swe-hero">
        <div class="swe-hero-content">
            <svg width="72" height="72" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" aria-label="Station8" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">
                <path d="M 50 14 C 30 14 30 42 50 50 C 70 58 70 86 50 86 C 30 86 30 58 50 50 C 70 42 70 14 50 14 Z"
                      stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="11" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <circle cx="50" cy="14" r="7" fill="#0d0d0d" stroke="#e6197f" stroke-width="4"/>
                <circle cx="50" cy="86" r="7" fill="#0d0d0d" stroke="#e6197f" stroke-width="4"/>
            </svg>
            <h1>Build durable<br>lines that never break.</h1>
            <p>
                <strong>Station</strong>은 노드 한 번의 실행, <strong>8</strong>은 옆으로 누이면 <strong>∞</strong>.
                cron으로 무한히 반복되고, 실패는 DLQ → 자동 재시도로. 멈추지 않는 자동화 루프를
                코드 또는 비주얼 빌더로 정의하세요.
            </p>
            <div class="swe-row">
                <a href="/line/builder" class="swe-btn-primary">+ Build a DAG</a>
                <a href="/line/dashboard" class="swe-btn-secondary">Open Dashboard →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features -->
    <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-3" style="margin-top: var(--space-section);">
        <div class="swe-card">
            <h3 class="swe-heading-md" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);">Visual DAG Builder</h3>
            <p class="swe-body-sm swe-mute" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);">
                Drag &amp; drop activities. Connect nodes. Save as a versioned definition.
            </p>
            <a href="/line/builder" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Open Builder</a>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-card">
            <h3 class="swe-heading-md" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);">Cron Scheduling</h3>
            <p class="swe-body-sm swe-mute" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);">
                Spring CronExpression. SKIP LOCKED 분산 워커. Pause / resume / run-now.
            </p>
            <a href="/line/schedules" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Open Schedules</a>
        </div>
        <div class="swe-card">
            <h3 class="swe-heading-md" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);">DLQ &amp; Monitoring</h3>
            <p class="swe-body-sm swe-mute" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);">
                Exponential backoff. Dead Letter Queue. Timeline viewer. Webhook alerts.
            </p>
            <a href="/line/dlq" class="swe-btn-tertiary swe-btn-sm">Open DLQ</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stack info -->
    <div class="swe-card-elevated" style="margin-top: var(--space-section);">
        <h3 class="swe-heading-md" style="margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);">Stack</h3>
        <div class="swe-grid swe-grid-3">
            <div>
                <div class="swe-caption swe-mute">Language / Framework</div>
                <div class="swe-body-md">Java 21 · Spring Boot 3.4</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="swe-caption swe-mute">Database</div>
                <div class="swe-body-md">Oracle / MariaDB (SKIP LOCKED)</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="swe-caption swe-mute">Adapter</div>
                <div class="swe-body-md">Spring Batch Job Runner</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
